    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution. This example boasts critical preventive maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe to address chassis torsional stress and a recently inspected VANOS system. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with aluminum control arms and fresh bushings, preserving the chassis's legendary communicative feedback. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the mechanical vitals remain stout, offering a linear power delivery and an 8,000 RPM redline that defines the golden era of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 31500.0,
