      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s looking for a brand new adventure! It\u2019s been super well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for those daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. The interior is nice and clean, and honestly, it still drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out with any questions; I\u2019d love to see this go to a great home!",
